## 🧪 Testing Requirements

- Unit tests: all `risk/` and `execution/` modules must have 100% coverage
- Integration tests: must test actual DB writes and reads (use test DB, not mocks)
- Backtest fixtures: use the same 3-month fixture dataset for all strategy tests
- Never mock the `RiskManager` in tests — test the real one
- CI gate: all tests must pass before merging to `main`
- Performance test: model inference must complete < 500ms (automated assertion)

